title: Threshold (001 - 008) (New 52) (2013) (Digital) (Empire)
description:
Threshold (001 - 008) (New 52) (2013) (Digital) (Empire) 

An intergalactic New 52 title, spinning out of the Green Lantern: New Guardians Annual starring an undercover Green Lantern named Jediah Caul. Larfleeze and Blue Beetle will make appearances. In August of 2013 the series was canceled to 8 issues also canceled in the series was Dial H for Hero series. Due to poor sales and marketing of the series.
